# ── Capacitor iOS Swift Package (generated) ─────────────────────────────
# CapApp-SPM is regenerated by `npx cap sync` on each machine and contains
# symlinks that Windows cannot create (EPERM). Committing it lets a Windows
# sync push broken/half-written symlink state that then breaks the Mac's
# iOS build. Treat it like node_modules: never tracked, always regenerated.
ios/App/CapApp-SPM/

# ── Secrets ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Apple APNs auth key — a private credential. Never commit.
*.p8
